         <abstract id="aspace_06d0ca0b0a3fac82bba19e3b9d6ae1f2">The collection is comprised of photographs of various Yale University academic buildings and New Haven, Connecticut scenes. The photographs were taken by Pach Brothers, the official university photographers for many of the late nineteenth-century Yale class albums.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <corpname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n93124968" source="naf">
               <part>Pach Brothers (Firm)</part>
            </corpname>
